:"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, I ask You for the health of my faith, such faith with good character, and salvation followed by success, Your mercy, Your wellness, Your forgiveness, and Your pleasure.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 8255 Grade: Hasan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37876,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/12\/afiyah-dunya-akhirah\/","url_meta":{"origin":5526,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Wellness: Success is well-being in this life and the next","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, which supplication is best?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cAsk your Lord for health and wellness in the world and in the Hereafter. If you are given wellness in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38968,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/03\/02\/ali-testifies-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":5526,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: Ali testifies for Abu Bakr and Umar","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 2, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Abdu Khayr reported: Ali, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cShall I not inform you of the best from this nation after its Prophet? It is Abu Bakr, and